    <item>
      <title>美国敦促墨西哥在两年内提高芯片产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/mexico-urged-by-us-to-boost-chip-production-within-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻墨西哥高级援助官员表示，墨西哥必须在未来两年加大对半导体行业的投资，以避免落后于竞争对手，并保证企业拥有充足的水和能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/mexico-urged-by-us-to-boost-chip-production-within-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 21:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
